CORRECTION OF A FORMER PAPER.

In the Philosophical Transactions for 1800,
P. 146, line 12, for 83810, read 84197;
——— line 15, for .0011562, read .0010116.
In Fig. 53, (Plate VII.) the Eb (Q.) is too near D;
and the Eb (Y) should be above, instead of below it.
